balance.fm (1.0.0) unstable; urgency=low

  * Initial release, based on balance 3.54
  * Add TCP keepalive configuration support
  * Fix and refactor logging/reporting code
  * Fix some off-by-one errors
  * Fix some inconsistent exit codes
  * Improve signal handling and shared memory handling
  * Improve shutdown behaviour
  * Added monitoring support
  * Documentation overhaul

